<plot>Dear Dad, is a short, documentary film about a daughter's emotional journey she portrays by reading a letter she wrote to her dad as she watches her strong, proud, Pro Football Hall of Famer, dad, Pete Pihos, deteriorate from Alzheimer's Disease. She recollects their past relationship prior to the disease by reading a letter he wrote to her at age 12.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?133643</url></doc>
